===Main characters===
;{{nihongo|Ange|アンジェ|Anje}}
:{{voiced by|[[Ayaka Imamura]]<ref name="Cast">{{cite web|url=http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2017-06-26/princess-principal-anime-ad-highlights-main-characters/.117989|title=Princess Principal Anime's Ad Highlights Main Characters|website=Anime News Network|date=June 26, 2017}}</ref>|Avery Smithhart<ref name="DubCast">{{cite web|url=https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2018-09-14/princess-principal-english-dub-cast-revealed/.136814|title=Princess Principal English Dub Cast Revealed|publisher=[[Anime News Network]]|date=September 14, 2018|accessdate=September 14, 2018}}</ref>}}
