'''World Cycling Day'''(also known as '''WCD''') is held annually on the 17th of September internationally. Its inception as the first global cycling cultural festival was celebrated in 2017, the year coincides with the 200th anniversary of the birth of [[bicycles]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.chinadaily.com.cn/business/2017-09/18/content_32161702.htm|title=Mobike, environmental groups announce World Cycling Day|publisher=chinadaily.com.cn}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bbrtv.com/2017/0918/350493.html|title=China’s bike-sharing giant initiates ‘World Cycling Day’ to promote green commuting|publisher=bbrtv.com}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://postcourier.com.pg/un-launches-world-cycling-day-mobike/|title=UN launches world cycling day with Mobike|publisher=postcourier.com.pg}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.thatsmags.com/guangzhou/post/20598/celebrate-world-cycling-day-in-guangzhou-this-weekend|title=Celebrate World Cycling Day This Weekend in Guangzhou|publisher=thatsmags.com}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://news.sina.com.cn/o/2017-09-17/doc-ifykyfwq7939104.shtml|title=9.17，就要骑！首个“世界骑行日”在深圳启动，今天你骑行了吗？|publisher=sina.com.cn}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://gb.cri.cn/42071/2017/09/06/7371s5248812.htm|title=摩拜与联合国环境署、新华社等发起“世界骑行日”|publisher=cri.cn}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://ent.163.com/17/0918/01/CUJ3CF2D000387GI.html|title=首个“世界骑行日”众星号召绿色出行|publisher=163.com}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://news.xinhuanet.com/photo/2017-09/17/c_1121677582.htm|title=世界骑行日”在京启动|publisher=xinhuanet.com}}</ref> == Background == The WCD is celebrated on Sep 17 annually, as the number “917” is the Chinese homonym of “Just Cycle”. On this day, the organizers appeal and advocate that citizens should pay close attention to cities’ sustainable development; take actions to reduce traffic congestion and air pollution by cycling instead of driving; feel and love the cities through riding bicycles, and make the cities a better place.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://news.163.com/17/0922/08/CUU2PGUL000187VI.html|title=世界骑行日：志愿者骑行宣传环保|publisher=163.com}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://world.huanqiu.com/hot/2017-09/11258689.html|title=把全球拽上自行车轮 世界骑行日中的中国共享单车模式|publisher=huanqiu.com}}</ref> == Themes == === 2017 - “Cycling Changes Cities” === The theme for WCD 2017 is “Cycling Changes Cities”. During the event, besides encouraging the users to travel by bicycles and promoting green travel, Mobike works with various organizations and business partners, user communities in more than 170 cities worldwide to organize rich online and offline activities, giving out various awards and virtual medals through its APP to encourage and attract more people to travel by bicycles in order to contribute to a low carbon, green and healthy city, and a pollution free earth.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://news.ifeng.com/a/20170919/52079349_0.shtml|title=骑行改变世界！摩拜发起“世界骑行日”获各界支持|publisher=ifeng.com}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://news.163.com/17/0918/15/CUKISU5L00018AOP.html|title=跨上摩拜邂逅众星，世界骑行日大家一起来绿色出行！|publisher=163.com}}</ref>
== Associated Events == Many international cities such as [[Singapore]], [[London]], [[Manchester]], [[Florence]], and [[Sapporo]] have participated actively in 2017’s WCD events, together with cities in China, to boost green and shared travels.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://finance.ifeng.com/a/20170929/15702921_0.shtml|title=摩拜单车发起世界骑行日，企业家、明星和名人积极响应|publisher=ifeng.com}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://news.ifeng.com/a/20170918/52062011_0.shtml|title=摩拜让骑行改变世界！世界骑行日网友纷纷晒出摩拜成就|publisher=ifeng.com}}</ref> == References == {{reflist}}
